Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落叶先生又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下明天早晨的打扫要辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边好像也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难道不能做些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起出门了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 去参加她们学校义卖会的预备会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义卖会?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起拿东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把它们卖掉 得到的钱用在学校上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个!

