Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...迷之生命体.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办义卖会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师 我们来办义卖会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖掉许多各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把得到的钱还给讨债的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把钱还清 就不用搬走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 好吗 义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么容易就能还得了的话 早就还了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比较大的学校办也许还能有些收入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种没几个学生的保育园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算办义卖会又能有多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办了也白办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我自顾自地激动起来...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打扫院子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全力以赴地办起义卖会来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果真的不行的话 最可怜的还是小鸠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白因为这个你才想让她放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那种说法可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话总是不顾忌别人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真成坏心眼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只顾自己兴高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生和清花老师都对我无话可说了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傻啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 傻是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那股拼命劲我觉得倒不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别搂着我 肉麻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来办吧 义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义卖会?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家里不要的东西或者自己制作的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带到保育园来卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是开店游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想开炒面店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是个好主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在联络簿上把详细情形写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回去给家里人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开什么样的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠又打起精神来了真是太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师 明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼哼~义卖会~哼哼哼哼哼哼哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(艾草保育园 义卖会)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小汪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得对不起狗和猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没说错所以没法反驳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小鸠画的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的鸭子和绵羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生 也会像那样笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(迷之生命体)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做这种小孩子一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很喜欢小鸠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君也是 那个人也是 都这么不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鸠 今天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义卖会的准备 明天再继续做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清花老师的丈夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得您曾经为您丈夫订过生日蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说那个人也不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和土鸠的画比起来还不算是谜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放晴娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴娃娃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢 是为了求晴天做来挂起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁拿来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈绪美做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的放晴娃娃很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远足的时候 去游泳池的时候都天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的放晴娃娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能卖出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能的 我也会做些东西带来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆在一起卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么给大家带来的东西贴上价签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能卖出去很多放晴娃娃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保育园就不会没掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢 我妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要生小宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说她虽然从这个月开始休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等小宝宝长大一点以后 又要开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候想把小宝宝再托给艾草保育园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 因为我是姐姐 会来保育园接他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样每天都能见到清花老师和小鸠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当姐姐的奈绪美 我也每天都想见到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(艾草保育园义卖会)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经非常晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾草保育园的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音 是之前接电话的小姑娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨债的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把保育园砸烂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还款期限不能延后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...电话里的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加班?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是贴义卖会的海报去了才这么晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是坏人 我才不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话的时候我就这么觉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我告诉清花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还款期限不能延后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今天我来了的事也帮我告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说期限一到 我就会把保育园砸烂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有小孩在也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想有人受伤 就赶紧搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说砸烂保育园 是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说有小孩在也一样 真是过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长着一张温和的脸 可是却让人觉得害怕 那个男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人?什么样的男人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤...藤本先生 你在听着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让我听到的 真是大声的自言自语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自言自语...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个什么样男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问他名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个笑眯眯的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还对清花老师直呼清花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冲浦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师碰见那家伙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没有 他跟我说完话就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙来过的事 不要告诉清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多说 照做就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把清花老师弄哭的话 饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不要再让清花老师见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫冲浦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟清花老师是什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很清楚了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花那家伙跟那个男人结婚了所以同姓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那家伙对清花直呼其名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶~~?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说那个人就是清花老师的丈夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么想要把保育园砸烂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要对这件事插手太多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 还有该做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果[瓶]不能装满
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能去你想去的地方了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 从刚开始就一直在缝什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用千岁小姐给的布缝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是企鹅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是兔子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是耳朵啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆 不管它是企鹅还是兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让义卖会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还打算量产啊 那个迷之物品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连五百祗先生都和藤本先生说一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(艾草保育园义卖会场)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天阴沉沉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 一定会放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿肯定能卖出去的东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天都加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴娃娃一定会让天气好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 可不要摔倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里边有饮料的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会摔倒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不会就是不会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人感情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 是藤本君从打工的地方拿来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还不是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太忘我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠果然还是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来呢 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家一起贴了海报的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈们可能会来的稍微晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有其他的客人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会就这样一个人都不来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为我提议办什么义卖会才...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠告诉我们以后 相当期待呢 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来份炒面如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要热咖啡也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千世和千帆也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看海报都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还担心是不是中止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那家伙干的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和大家说义卖会没有中止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去说已经太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会晚 说不定会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算来了 像这样规模的义卖会...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 哪怕一个人也好我也希望多些人来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家努力办的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好孩子 小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说去叫人了嘛 我去准备咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很坦率但也是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是没有人来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨也停了 太阳也都出来了的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义卖会是在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鸠小姐通知我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里有开义卖会?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么稀罕物件吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鸠告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠呢?还没回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一杯冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老师 一份冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位元气十足的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边跑一边大声喊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾草保育园有义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有义卖会~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她那么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住说 是吗 等下我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就握着我的手不停地挥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以想象呢 确实像小鸠的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来的晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义卖会来了好多客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气转好了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾草保育园有义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位务必赏光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾草保育园有义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位务必赏光

Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}下一话[...谜之生命体.2号.]

Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:07.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:14.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:22.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:49.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:53.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:24:00.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:05.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:09.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:14.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:27.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:07.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人们都是那么想飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:14.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不过被重力所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:22.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其实谁都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那个孩子为什么如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也许是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:49.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能对你说 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:53.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看见你的笑容 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:24:00.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}来来往往中 变得愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:05.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:09.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:14.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:27.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜极而泣总是那么不可思议
